The paper focuses on developing an automated claim extraction system for scientific publications, specifically in the biomedical domain. The proposed model uses deep learning techniques and transfer learning, which are commonly used in natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) research, falling under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
